Package com.adobe.livecycle.readerextensions.client

The com.adobe.livecycle.readerextensions.client package enables you to easily share interactive PDF documents with external parties by extending the functionality of Adobe Reader.

See:
          Description

Class Summary
ReaderExtensionsConstants Constants used in the ReaderExtensions DSC.
ReaderExtensionsConstants.Permissions ReaderExtensions Permission.
ReaderExtensionsConstants.ResourceTypes Resource types for ReaderExtensions.
ReaderExtensionsConstants.Roles ReaderExtensions Role.
ReaderExtensionsOptionSpec Represents run-time options that are available when applying usage rights to a PDF document.
ReaderExtensionsServiceClient Enables the creation of a Java object that invokes operations that belong to the Reader Extensions service.
RESMsgSet This class contains error messages logged by the ReaderExtensions Service using the "RES-" category.
 

Exception Summary
CredentialException Credential-related exceptions for the Reader Extensions service.
CredentialServiceUnavailableException Exceptions related to using TrustStore for the Reader Extensions service.
ProcessingException Credential-related exceptions for the Reader Extensions service.
ReaderExtensionsException Represents the base class for exceptions that are thrown by the Reader Extensions service.
 

Package com.adobe.livecycle.readerextensions.client Description

The com.adobe.livecycle.readerextensions.client package enables you to easily share interactive PDF documents with external parties by extending the functionality of Adobe Reader.

For information about using this package to extend the functionality of Adobe Reader, see Applying Usage Rights.
